Package: ttb.gov
Title: Alcohol and Tobacco Tax and Trade Bureau (TTB) Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for TTB public data. Covers permit lookups, formula processing times, COLA label processing times, and permit data by type.
